  <summary>4/15/2015--Introduced.
No Bonuses for Tax Delinquent IRS Employees Act of 2015

 Prohibits the payment of&#160;any performance award (including, but not limited to, bonuses, step increases, and time off) to an employee of the Internal Revenue Service who owes an outstanding federal tax debt.</summary>
